" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"見仁見智<br />\n不過，係我個人嘅角度睇落，係真係無用<br />\n首先，個老師所做嘅，所展示嘅嘢係唔係啱，呢個對一個無認知嘅人就已經係一個問號。<br />\n撇除呢一點唔講，最大個問題就係你跟住網路教學去學習之後，你所做出嚟嘅嘢，係無途徑比你知道你做嘅嘢係啱定係錯......<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(所以我嘅TG免費問事+聲音診斷就係為此而存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n不過其實最重要嘅，係首先要了解自己需要學尐乜<br />\n係呢個時代資訊咁發達嘅社會中，要搵學習嘅資源實在唔難<br />\n不過你自己如果唔知自己需要從邊方面下手提升自己嘅話，咁再多嘅教學都係徒然。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca31d0db5052a6e0ad1d3c01f586410ea2b1e6a3","tid":2445787,"uid":302951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"35b19de26131b239c815270f62874c3968e53ea5","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3adf051645a57b612e47e6f5208a99e789bd9c","tid":2445787,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"追咗巴打之前嘅po 好有心教 <br />\n留個靚名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有唔明嘅可以隨時問嫁~"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"啱啱沖涼隨口唱歌 醒起自己一上高音 一係好似合唱團咁吊高把聲 一係喉嚨太用力 好似嗌咁 把聲好難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見啲歌手都係用真聲用力唱 但係聽落唔「銀」耳 仲覺得好有爆發性 渲染到情緒<br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8089843925718b41a34d241879bdc5e5666225a5","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca31d0db5052a6e0ad1d3c01f586410ea2b1e6a3","tid":2445787,"uid":302951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"35b19de26131b239c815270f62874c3968e53ea5","tid":2445787,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3adf051645a57b612e47e6f5208a99e789bd9c","tid":2445787,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,